content: Perfect! Does exactly what you need it too! Very smooth as well!
Awesome for keeping track and looking back at who won which games.
Very nice app, would be helpful to be able to edit an item in the history instead of having to remove and re-add it.

Best phase 10 score keeper. Worth the price. Don't waste your time with the free versions. This also let's you pick Phase 10 variations (amazing for sure), can have multiple games started, tracks dealer, can title each game and it has the list of phases so you can see what uou need. Great job!!!
